  </head>

  <body>
    <Header>
      <div
        class="mt-6 pt-4 sm:pt-8 md:pt-12 font-display text-center flex justify-center"
      >
        <img
          src="/oobavi3.svg"
          class="w-32 h-32 lg:w-48 lg:h-48 rounded-full bg-amber-800 dark:bg-indigo-900"
          alt={`Cartoon render based on my Ooblets character.`}
        />
      </div>
    </Header>
    <div class="mx-safe px-4 md:p-6 lg:px-12 my-4">
      <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <section
          class="prose-all prose-indigo mx-auto lg:-rotate-2 shadow-layered-light bg-white dark:shadow-layered-dark dark:bg-slate-800 px-6 py-4 lg:px-8 rounded-xl lg:rounded-3xl"
        >
          <p
            class="flex items-center justify-center text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display text-indigo-500 dark:text-indigo-400"
          >
            Hello!
            <span class="ml-2" aria-label="Waving hand."> ðŸ‘‹ </span>
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm a weird nerd that tinkers in all things computers.
            Professionally, I'm a web app developer, but I also do a lot of UI
            design, server setup, and really anything computery. I have some
            neat cats too. I'm on <a href="https://github.com/Alanaktion"
              >GitHub</a
            >,
            <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/alan.pizza">Bluesky</a>,
            <a href="https://keybase.io/alanaktion">Keybase</a>, and
            <a href="https://last.fm/user/Alanaktion">Last.fm</a>, and probably
            other places too.
          </p>
        </section>

        <hr />

        <Unsplash />

        <section
          class="prose-all prose-indigo mx-auto lg:mb-12 lg:rotate-2 shadow-layered-light bg-white dark:shadow-layered-dark dark:bg-slate-800 px-6 py-4 lg:px-8 rounded-xl lg:rounded-3xl"
        >
          <p>
            I also run a <a href="https://alan.pizza">pizza blog</a>! I eat a
            lot of pizza (like, <i>too much</i> pizza), so I decided to document
            it. For a while when I first started the blog, I posted every time I
            ate pizza, but since that's often daily, I now only post new pizzas that
            I try for the first time. I try to give a simple review of each one,
            and while I find detailed food critique weird and difficult to do well,
            I enjoy writing the brief summary and posting the photos.
          </p>
          <div class="sm:flex gap-4 lg:gap-6 items-center">
            <picture>
              <source
                type="image/avif"
                srcset="https://alan.pizza/img/7xXDVJxNyD-800.avif 800w"
              />
              <source
                type="image/webp"
                srcset="https://alan.pizza/img/7xXDVJxNyD-800.webp 800w"
              />
              <img
                class="rounded-sm mx-auto sm:w-64 my-2! text-sm aspect-[4/3]"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                src="https://alan.pizza/img/7xXDVJxNyD-800.jpeg"
                alt="A pizza in the box, half is pepperoni pizza and half is cheese breadsticks."
              />
            </picture>
            <div>
              <p>
                My current favorite pizza is the Little Caesarâ€™s Slices-N-Stix.
                Half-pizza, half-Italian Cheese Bread!
              </p>
              <p>
                <a
                  class="font-display inline-flex items-center gap-1"
                  href="https://alan.pizza/2022/09/01/little-caesars-slices-n-stix/"
                >
                  View Post â†’
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr />

        <Portfolio
          class="lg:mb-12 py-4 lg:py-6 -mx-4 px-4 glass text-slate-50 rounded-3xl backdrop-blur-xs"
        />
      </main>
    </div>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
